{"tid":1770523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】彈劾特首林鄭月娥","createTime":"2019-12-05T09:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T09:58:14.000Z","uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb705f7092d6b890a057a4c28a87741b4dfa8d1","tid":1770523,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191205/60343857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60343857&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=f0d128dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60343857&h=f03f69d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191205/60343857</a><br />\n立法會今早繼續辯論彈劾特首林鄭月娥的議案。建制派至今未有人發言，民主派則連番炮轟港府、林鄭自硬推「送中」惡法以來種種不是，包括不聽民意、言而無信、縱容警暴，強調要止暴制亂，必先遏制警暴、獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n快啲發長輩圖迫民建聯班契弟彈劾埋一份<br />\n要民生, 唔要催淚彈, 唔要林鄭月娥 !"},{"pid":"cba89e5c558b59ce8715a47a643dfb634e49e4ec","tid":1770523,"uid":322955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"彈劾過了或是不信任過了<br />\n<br />\n如果中央不同意怎算<br />\n<br />\n這個制度設計很奇怪耶<br />\n如果是民選首長<br />\n就算是間接民意只要議會一致通過就要下台了<br />\n關中央屁事<br />\n<br />\n難不成一個萬人討厭的特首不能罷免<br />\n這什麼怪制度"}]}